{
  "id": "e385d55a6e074620a42592dc5fe615e8",
  "title": "Addon for Advanced Field Of Vision",
  "description": "Addon for Advanced Field Of Vision, unlocks - Night Mode. Your NPCs can now see the enemy in lighting areas",
  "longDescription": "<p>Night Mode <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gmM6YvBn9WV-xbTgW2R4SFVW9jUjk0nm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo build</a> - you can try this</p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/GMzNVTXQIKo?si&#61;GSCvu-CNDEG1Jq5P\" rel=\"nofollow\">Short video</a></p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"https://redirect.epicgames.com/?redirectTo&#61;https://discord.gg/p8NbUxPBxM\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord Server and support</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Important: </strong></p><ul><li><strong>The add-on requires the main product to work.</strong></li><li><strong>This is an add-on for the product </strong><a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/advanced-field-of-vision\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Advanced Field of Vision</strong></a><strong> .</strong></li><li><strong>The add-on is installed on top of the main product with confirmation of file replacement.</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Description of mechanics:</p><ul><li>Adds lighted zone to the FoV</li><li>The NPC has a limited visibility range and only reacts to what is nearby.</li><li>The lighting area expands the vision area</li><li>The NPC takes into account all functionality in the lighting zone in the same way as in the inner area (Close area)</li><li>Has the most accurate repetition of shadows from the light point.</li><li>The light source is interactive and can be turned on/off by the player.</li></ul><p><br /></p><ul><li>3 types of lighting based on Point Light:</li></ul><ol><li>Point Light - parent class</li><li>Campfire - child</li><li>Light on the barrel - child</li></ol><p><br /></p><p>Easy installation.</p><p>Night mode can be combined with normal mode.</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p><strong>Simple installation instructions:</strong></p><ul><li>Open the launcher</li><li>Select product Advanced Field Of Vision</li><li>Add a Advanced Field Of Vision to your project</li><li>Then add the addition to the same project.</li><li>That&#39;s it.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 6</p><p>Input: (not required)</p><p>Network Replicated: (No)</p><p>Main Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuItE7EyCpexXpMt0A_3gfov_iQlVUI_mHspz4suyxk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Link</a></p>",
